<p>
<h2>The Formal Gardens</h2>
<p>
The formal gardens (rarely just &quot;gardens&quot;, because there are
other gardens elsewhere, notably outside the cottage) are a nice, if
knotty collection of rooms that are fairly newbie-safe. There <i>is</i>
some treasure scattered around, but very little. There's also some
easy-to-handle wildlife which wanders leisurely about (here and in the park to the
west) that newbies like to practise their fighting skills on. Watch out for the <font color="#00ee00">maze of hedges</font>,
because it's very easy to get lost there and the out
command doesn't work once you're in it.
<p>
